Why not?

4
00:01:41,821 --> 00:01:44,091
For one thing, he's an excellent champ.

5
00:01:44,478 --> 00:01:46,683
At least try to get some sleep.

6
00:01:46,910 --> 00:01:49,300
If I were you, no more Congnac.

7
00:01:49,503 --> 00:01:51,414
We'll come for you at five.
It'd give you three hours.

8
00:01:51,616 --> 00:01:53,045
You will be here.

9
00:01:53,249 --> 00:01:55,519
I don't mind so much to being killed.

10
00:01:55,874 --> 00:02:00,348
But you know how it is for
me to get up in the morning.

11
00:02:00,708 --> 00:02:01,057
Good night.

12
00:02:01,283 --> 00:02:04,099
Good night.

13
00:02:07,878 --> 00:02:12,102
I'm afraid this time, Stephan has picked
a fight with the wrong man

14
00:02:12,295 --> 00:02:17,217
I wonder if he'll be here
when we come back?

15
00:02:17,417 --> 00:02:18,180
Who is it?

16
00:02:18,377 --> 00:02:19,108
Brown.

17
00:02:19,337 --> 00:02:24,074
Good morning, Mr. Brown.

18
00:02:37,519 --> 00:02:39,145
Cheer up, John.

19
00:02:39,343 --> 00:02:42,410
This is one engagement
that I have no intention of keeping.

20
00:02:42,608 --> 00:02:45,958
Honor is a luxury.
Only gentleman can afford.

21
00:02:46,194 --> 00:02:47,656
Pack my things...

22
00:02:47,859 --> 00:02:53,359
Whatever you think
that I'll need for a indefinite stay.

23
00:02:53,556 --> 00:02:55,444
I have a cab downstairs...

24
00:02:55,669 --> 00:03:00,110
In about an hour,
I'll go out the back way.

25
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:06,007
I'm sorry.
I won't be here to see their faces.

26
00:03:10,425 --> 00:03:13,623
Has this come during the night?

27
00:03:13,818 --> 00:03:19,516
Would you bring me
some coffee... with Congnac?

28
00:04:21,392 --> 00:04:26,128
By the time you read this letter,
I may be dead.

29
00:04:26,481 --> 00:04:30,760
I have so much to tell you,
perhaps very little time.

30
00:04:30,963 --> 00:04:32,491
Will I ever send it?

31
00:04:32,724 --> 00:04:36,500
I don't know.

32
00:04:37,973 --> 00:04:42,382
I must find strength to write
before it's too late.

33
00:04:42,743 --> 00:04:47,087
And as I write, it became clear
that what happened to us

34
00:04:47,288 --> 00:04:51,600
