our poor understanding.

35
00:04:51,834 --> 00:04:53,296
If this reaches you...

36
00:04:53,530 --> 00:04:55,286
You'll know how I became yours...

37
00:04:55,483 --> 00:05:00,122
When you didn't know who I was,
or even that I existed.

38
00:05:00,316 --> 00:05:05,053
I think everyone has two birthdays.
Day of his physical bir

