van in front of our building.

44
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,554
I wander about in our new neighbor...

45
00:05:39,753 --> 00:05:41,925
Who owned such beautiful things.

46
00:05:42,282 --> 00:05:44,704
Lisa! Come in, Lisa!

47
00:05:44,907 --> 00:05:48,585
Come in this minute, did you hear?

48
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:50,184
Lisa!

49
