64
00:06:42,077 --> 00:06:44,085
Lisa, what are you doing out there?

65
00:06:44,317 --> 00:06:47,133
Come inside.

66
00:07:00,578 --> 00:07:04,802
I didn't see you that day,
or from many days that day after

67
00:07:05,027 --> 00:07:10,725
But I could listen to your playing.

68
00:07:36,013 --> 00:07:38,054
I wish he stop that noise.

69
00:07:38,415 --> 00:07:40,270
