77
00:08:06,167 --> 00:08:08,078
Oh.

78
00:08:08,312 --> 00:08:10,549
You know the boy
I was talking to outside the school?

79
00:08:10,905 --> 00:08:14,222
The bony one with the yellow
hair and a long nose.

80
00:08:14,458 --> 00:08:16,630
One who lives next to the grocery.

81
00:08:16,827 --> 00:08:18,136
