If he dosen't keep his hands to himself.

83
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:27,579
The things he does,
Right out in the street

84
00:09:05,002 --> 00:09:10,121
Thank you, John.
I'll be home later.

85
00:09:19,151 --> 00:09:21,966
Thank you.

86
00:09:22,511 --> 00:09:25,327
Good morning.

87
00:09:35,603 --> 00:09:41,202
