I'll get you for that!

90
00:09:46,263 --> 00:09:48,205
Yes, I was blushing.

91
00:09:48,408 --> 00:09:50,994
And hard as it
may be for you to realize...

92
00:09:51,193 --> 00:09:55,537
From that moment on,
I was in love with you.

93
00:09:55,738 --> 00:09:59,034
Quite consciously,
I was preparing myself for you.

94
00:09:59,387 --> 00:10:03,829
I kept my clothes neater,
so you wouldn't be ashamed of me.

95
00:10:04,189 --> 00:10:05,782
Bow, two three four...

96
00:10:06,141 --> 00:10:07,702
