Sorry, mother.

112
00:11:42,044 --> 00:11:46,236
But I really lived for
those evenings when you're alone.

113
00:11:46,429 --> 00:11:52,127
And I pretended
that you're playing just for me.

114
00:12:05,763 --> 00:12:07,618
I know you didn't know it...

115
00:12:07,972 --> 00:12:13,670
You're giving me some
of the happiest hours of my life.

116
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:33,239
Then came a great day for me.

117
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:35,131
In the building where we lived.

118
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:41,058
