142
00:16:59,937 --> 00:17:02,938
Come dear, I've something to tell you.

143
00:17:03,330 --> 00:17:06,462
It's really good news.

144
00:17:06,659 --> 00:17:13,568
If you think about it sensibly,
you'll be very happy.

145
00:17:13,925 --> 00:17:16,773
Sit down.

146
00:17:28,042 --> 00:17:29,569
I can understand
that you must've been startled...

147
00:17:29,802 --> 00:17:32,323
