her customer and me in the hall.

148
00:17:32,523 --> 00:17:37,161
Perhaps it's my fault for not telling
you something about it

149
00:17:37,357 --> 00:17:41,188
You see, dear,
your mother is not really old.

150
00:17:41,390 --> 00:17:42,405
