156
00:17:58,611 --> 00:18:01,579
It links... a military tailor.

157
00:18:01,940 --> 00:18:07,638
And he's down here
to ask me to marry him.

158
00:18:09,047 --> 00:18:11,950
Besides, he is a kind man,
and he likes you very much.

159
