208
00:19:56,345 --> 00:20:00,208
Suddenly I knew
I couldn't live without you.

209
00:20:00,442 --> 00:20:02,232
I didn't know what I had in mind, or...

210
00:20:02,426 --> 00:20:05,329
...what my parents would do
when they found me missing.

211
00:20:05,692 --> 00:20:08,792
All I wanted was to see you once more.

212
00:20:08,988 --> 00:20:09,719
To be near you again.

213
00:20:09,917 --> 00:20:13,912
